Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法  空中飄浮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:52.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【很遺憾  萎人  很遺憾】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我唱一首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌名是…啊啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.49,0:23:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村長？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The 河童2  隨波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了  村長的即興搞笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是村長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  No.1！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.1！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白臉~小白臉~小白臉~小白~臉~小白剪子布！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.27,0:23:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白臉猜拳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸的人要當贏的人的小白臉  一輩子背負這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這猜拳猜得也太沉重了吧！
